"""
NEURAL NODE TEMPLATE ATTACHMENT & RELEASE OF INFORMATION SYSTEM
===============================================================
Complete system for:
1. Attaching templates to physical/digital entities
2. Controlling release of information from templates
3. Creating verifiable "Release of Notes" for data sharing
4. Maintaining chain of custody for template-derived data

Attachments can be to:
- Smart Contracts (blockchain)
- Digital Wallets (crypto/NFT)
- Medical Records (EHR/EMR)
- Research Datasets
- Marketing Profiles
- IoT Devices
- Biometric Scanners
"""

